<plot>In the first-ever video game, two players play a video version of table tennis. The ball bounces off the walls and the paddles. The paddles are controlled by the players by using the paddle knobs on the machine. When a ball gets by one player's paddle, the other player scores a point. When someone scores 11 points, they win and it's game over.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?438334</url></doc>
